\c 40
\s UJosefa uchasisa amaphupho
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kwalezizinto umphathinkezo\x + Neh. 1.11.\x* wenkosi yeGibithe lomphekizinkwa bona enkosini yabo, enkosini yeGibithe.
\v 2 Ngakho uFaro wabathukuthelela abathenwa bakhe ababili\x + 37.36.\x*, induna yabaphathinkezo lenduna yabaphekizinkwa.
\v 3 Wazinikela esitokisini\x + 39.20.\x*, endlini yenduna yabalindi\x + 37.36.\x*, entolongweni, indawo lapho uJosefa ayebotshelwe khona.
\v 4 Induna yabalindi yasimlaya uJosefa ukuba lazo\x + 39.4,5.\x*, wazisebenzela; njalo zaba lensuku esitokisini.
\p
\v 5 Zombili zaseziphupha amaphupho, ngamunye iphupho lakhe, ngabusuku bunye, ngamunye njengengcazelo yephupho lakhe, umphathinkezo lomphekizinkwa ababengabenkosi yeGibithe ababebotshiwe entolongweni.
\v 6 UJosefa wasengena kibo ekuseni, wababona, khangela-ke, benyukumele.
\v 7 Wasebabuza abathenwa bakaFaro ababelaye esitokisini endlini yenkosi yakhe, esithi: Kungani ubuso benu budanile lamuhla?
\v 8 Basebesithi kuye: Siphuphile iphupho, njalo kakho umchasisi walo\x + 41.15.\x*. UJosefa wasesithi kubo: Ingcazelo kayisizo zikaNkulunkulu yini\x + 41.16. Dan. 2.28,47.\x*? Ake lingilandisele \add wona\add*.
\v 9 Induna yabaphathinkezo yalandisa iphupho layo kuJosefa, yathi kuye: Ephutsheni lami, khangela-ke, kwakukhona ivini phambi kwami;
\v 10 evinini-ke kwakukhona ingatsha ezintathu; njalo kwakungathi liyahluma, impoko zalo zaphuma, amahlukuzo alo athela izithelo zevini ezivuthiweyo.
\v 11 Njalo inkezo kaFaro yayisesandleni sami; ngasengithatha izithelo zevini, ngazikhamela enkezweni kaFaro, nganika inkezo esandleni sikaFaro.
\v 12 UJosefa wasesithi kuyo: Le yingcazelo yalo\x + 40.18; 41.12. Dan. 2.36; 5.16.\x*. Ingatsha ezintathu ziyizinsuku ezintathu\x + 40.18; 41.26.\x*;
\v 13 kusesephakathi kwensuku ezintathu uFaro uzaphakamisa ikhanda lakho, akubuyisele esikhundleni sakho\x + 2 Kho. 25.27. Jer. 52.31. 40.19,21,22. Hlab. 3.3.\x*; njalo uzanika inkezo kaFaro esandleni sakhe, njengendlela yakuqala lapho wawungumphathinkezo wakhe.
\v 14 Kodwa ungikhumbule lawe, lapho uhlezi kuhle, ake ungenzele umusa\x + Josh. 2.12. 1 Sam. 20.14. 2 Sam. 9.1. 1 Kho. 2.7.\x*, ungibike kuFaro, ungikhuphe kulindlu.
\v 15 Ngoba ngebiwa lokwebiwa elizweni lamaHeberu, lalapha futhi kangenzanga lutho ukuze bangifake emgodini\x + 39.20.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Lapho induna yabaphekizinkwa ibona ukuthi uchasise kuhle, yathi kuJosefa: Lami bengisephutsheni; khangela-ke, bekukhona izitsha ezintathu zilezinkwa ezimhlophe\f + \fk zilezinkwa ezimhlophe: \fl kumbe, \fq ezilezobhobo.\f* ekhanda lami;
\v 17 njalo esitsheni esingaphezulu kwakukhona okokudla konke kukaFaro, umsebenzi obhakiweyo; njalo inyoni zakudla lokho esitsheni esisekhanda lami.
\v 18 UJosefa wasephendula wathi: Le yingcazelo yalo\x + 40.12.\x*. Izitsha ezintathu ziyizinsuku ezintathu;
\v 19 kusesephakathi kwensuku ezintathu uFaro uzaphakamisa ikhanda lakho\x + 40.13.\x* lisuke kuwe, akulengise esihlahleni; inyoni zizakudla inyama yakho ziyisuse kuwe.
\p
\v 20 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesithathu, usuku lokuzalwa kukaFaro\x + Mat. 14.6. Mark. 6.21.\x*, wenzela inceku zakhe zonke idili; waphakamisa ikhanda\x + 40.13,19.\x* lenduna yabaphathinkezo lekhanda lenduna yabaphekizinkwa phakathi kwenceku zakhe.
\v 21 Wayibuyisela induna yabaphathinkezo\x + 40.13.\x* ekuphatheni kwayo inkezo; yasinika inkezo esandleni sikaFaro\x + Neh. 2.1.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa wayilengisa induna yabaphekizinkwa\x + 40.19.\x*, njengoba uJosefa ezichasisele.
\v 23 Kodwa induna yabaphathinkezo kayimkhumbulanga uJosefa, kodwa yamkhohlwa.
